org.opengrok.indexer.analysis

Interface JFlexJointLexer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    JFlexLexer, JFlexStackingLexer
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AdaSymbolTokenizer, AdaXref, EiffelSymbolTokenizer, EiffelXref, HCLLexer, HCLSymbolTokenizer, HCLXref, JavaScriptLexer, JavaScriptSymbolTokenizer, JavaScriptXref, PerlSymbolTokenizer, PerlXref, PLSQLSymbolTokenizer, PLSQLXref, RubySymbolTokenizer, RubyXref, SQLSymbolTokenizer, SQLXref, TerraformSymbolTokenizer, TerraformXref, TypeScriptSymbolTokenizer, TypeScriptXref, VerilogSymbolTokenizer, VerilogXref

    public interface JFlexJointLexer
extends JFlexStackingLexer
    Represents an API for JFlex lexers that produce multiple types of derived OpenGrok documents (e.g., cross-reference documents [xrefs] or Lucene search documents [tokenizers]) from the same JFlex productions.
